<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Letter Book Copy: letters copied into a bound letter-book ]">LB</abbr>, <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ New York Public Library, New York ]">NN</span>: Schuyler Papers.
</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0509-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0509-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Richard Montgomery wrote to Schuyler on 24 Nov.: I have not I believe more than 800 Effectives hereHowever I can have as many Canadians as I know how to ma[i]ntain at least I think so while affairs ware so promising an aspect (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>). See also <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0469&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-02-02-0469-fn-0002#GEWN-03-02-02-0469-fn-0002" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 8 Dec. 1775, n.2</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0509-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0509-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>For the negotiations at Albany, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0469" class="document">Schuyler to GW, 8 Dec. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0509-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0509-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>Schuyler enclosed extracts of his letters of 11, 18, 20, 2728 Nov. and 8 Dec., which are in <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>.</p>

</div>
